      <title>黑石集团的葛瑞预计增长将在通胀斗争中放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/blackstone-s-gray-sees-growth-slowing-as-fed-battles-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑石公司总裁乔恩·格雷表示，由于顽固的通货膨胀会影响美联储开始降低借贷成本的能力，经济增长将会放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/blackstone-s-gray-sees-growth-slowing-as-fed-battles-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 01:02:16 GMT</pubDate>
